{"tid":2059822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZONE MV預告爆發爭議 總攻中的外國粉絲們","createTime":"2020-06-11T07:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T09:17:04.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f936b678c9077057a4f5f053dbf382278f9ce0d6","tid":2059822,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:48:05.000Z","msg":"因為IZONE預告問題，總攻中的外國粉絲們<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HiTqRYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHiTqRYD.jpg&h=602e0ca6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snNZWqx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnNZWqx.gif&h=de91542c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n致Off The Record和Swing娛樂。<br />\n綜合多種意見，經過深思熟慮後，以跟&ldquo;幻想童話&rdquo;預告相關的理由給予聯絡。<br />\n預告中IZONE隊長權恩妃頭上佩戴了類似BINDI寶石的飾品，BINDI寶石是印度教的神聖寶石，即使只是佩戴也是無禮的行為<br />\n這是個嚴重的問題，我們海外WIZ*ONE希望IZONE工作人員能承認這一問題並儘快給予反饋。希望IZONE的造型師和規劃團隊以後也不要再出現此類問題，WIZ*ONE中包含著多種種族和文化，希望能給予尊重。<br />\n謝謝。"},{"pid":"eae9ebbebd013d26359e05bd63155815f40930fc","tid":2059822,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"好能小事姐🚬"},{"pid":"83257d259bd361d3b030f54b9add3bb72d07f6c1","tid":2059822,"uid":219225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"印狗麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0725fa8a8aebb880a4390d930e80ccb51ac69972","tid":2059822,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"83257d259bd361d3b030f54b9add3bb72d07f6c1","tid":2059822,"uid":219225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"印狗麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"印狗真係垃圾黎"},{"pid":"2d8b24a4bbd0b708cd36a2d06df03b30df464c56","tid":2059822,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"扮下綱手都唔得？"},{"p